9
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:24,200
OUTSIDERS

10
00:00:24,279 --> 00:00:25,320
It was said

11
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,599
that many years ago,

12
00:00:26,680 --> 00:00:27,680
several Outsiders

13
00:00:27,759 --> 00:00:28,880
discovered the Eight Supremes

14
00:00:28,959 --> 00:00:30,520
in a mysterious place.

15
00:00:30,599 --> 00:00:32,040
Those eight abilities,

16
00:00:32,119 --> 00:00:33,480
endowed with immense power,

17
00:00:33,559 --> 00:00:36,559
tore the Outsiders' world asunder.

18
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:38,519
To obtain those abilities,

19
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:40,400
