20
00:00:40,480 --> 00:00:41,720
among each other.

21
00:00:42,559 --> 00:00:44,480
It took place during the Year of Jiashen,

22
00:00:44,559 --> 00:00:45,600
and thus it was called

23
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:47,640
the Jiashen Calamity.

24
00:00:48,239 --> 00:00:50,879
Following the deaths or disappearances of several legendary figures,

25
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,280
the secret was left buried.

26
00:00:52,919 --> 00:00:54,680
The wheel of time continues to turn.

27
00:00:54,760 --> 00:00:55,879
Peace is about to be broken.

28
00:00:56,519 --> 00:00:57,919
Our story

29
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,959
begins one evening.

30
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:10,800
What a bunch of jerks!

31
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:12,840
