163
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:24,319
I shall let you two catch up.

164
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:25,880
Let's go.

165
00:09:25,959 --> 00:09:27,079
-Yes! -Come on!

166
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,160
